          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The owner of the C7 Corvette that’s still missing is angry about the situation. “What’s going to happen to them (the thieves)? A slap on the wrist? The owner is the one stuck with the burden of everything.”",
