      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Obviously, in this situation the owner couldn’t have done more to secure their vehicle. However, this is yet another reminder that you should garage your car whenever possible, especially at night, and think of investing in some extra security measures to make it less enticing for thieves. Car theft is still sky-high in many areas, with performance vehicles and classic cars being prime targets.",
